Mnemonic:
All People Seem To Need Data Processing

🛠️ Task 1 – Network Interfaces

Show interfaces:

ip addr

or

ip a

Show link status:

ip link
🛠️ Task 2 – Routing Table
ip route

or

route -n

Default gateway:

ip route | grep default
🛠️ Task 3 – DNS Troubleshooting

Check DNS:

cat /etc/resolv.conf

Lookup:

nslookup google.com
dig google.com

Reverse lookup:

dig -x 8.8.8.8
